trans-unit.source: Determines the output files for non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer output-filene for ikke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjektet referanser.

trans-unit.source: The `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` task searches for a special property set by the [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] IDE for the list of project GUIDs and their associated outputs.
trans-unit.target: Den `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` oppgave Søk etter en spesiell egenskap som er angitt av det [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] IDE for listen over prosjektet GUIDer og de tilknyttede utdataene.

trans-unit.source: The IDE only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects and in this way separates [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references from non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] references.
trans-unit.target: IDE over løser bare ikke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjekter, og dermed mellom [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjektet referanser fra ikke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] referanser.

trans-unit.source: The IDE returns the list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects as UnresolvedProjectReferences.
trans-unit.target: IDE returnerer listen over [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjektene som UnresolvedProjectReferences.

trans-unit.source: This enables the task to use more powerful [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] mechanisms to manipulate just the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references, such as.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør det mulig at oppgaven skal bruke mer kraftige [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] mekanismer til å behandle bare den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjektet refererer til, for eksempel.

trans-unit.source: calling into specific targets of references to get the manifest file name, which would not be possible with a mixed list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] and non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references.
trans-unit.target: kall til bestemte målene for referanser til å hente navnet på manifestfilen, som ikke mulig med blandet liste over [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] og ikke-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjektet referanser.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en XML-streng som inneholder løst prosjektet utdataene.

trans-unit.target: Et XML-streng som inneholder løse prosjektet utdataene.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir løst referanse baner som beholde de opprinnelige referanseattributter for prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets project reference items that are in the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir prosjektet referanse elementer som i det [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.

trans-unit.source: Since [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects, the project reference items that could not be resolved using the pre-resolved list of outputs are in the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
trans-unit.target: Siden [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] før løser ikke -[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] prosjekter, prosjektet referanse-elementer som ikke kan løses ved hjelp av listen over løst av utdataene er i den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
